org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM spree_stores INNER JOIN spree_products_stores ON spree_stores.id = spree_products_stores.store_id WHERE spree_stores.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products_stores.product_id = "$1" LIMIT 1

rewrites.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM spree_stores WHERE spree_stores.deleted_at IS NULL LIMIT 1
